data.description: This charming home featuring 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, RV access and Owned Solar!. Hardwood and tile floors throughout. the home, The kitchen offers granite counters and stainless steel appliances. On either side of the kitchen you'll find the living room and dining room. Two spare bedrooms - one offers a step in closet and the other dual closets. Primary bedroom offers a walk-in closet, private access to/from the backyard, and private restroom with step in shower. The backyard offers a studio for potential passive income., detached 2 car garage, citrus tree, and large gazebo ideal for entertaining! . This home sits within walking distance from Willow Glen Park, has easy freeway access, many shopping centers nearby, and Willow Glen Elementary School nearby.
